description:
Hello, I'm Agatha and merry christmas! 🎄

In this video, It's going to be a makeup get ready with me for the holiday season! This look is perfect if you want to look festive this Christmas 🥰 I hope my video helped you in some way 😊 if you do have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

Products used:
Fit me foundation in 128 wam nude
The Saem tip concealer in 02
Vice Cosmetics duo finish foundation in putinamez
Detail Cosmetics SuperFine Liner in Mocha
Eb Advance face trio in fig
Vice cosmetics x Anne Clutz eyeshadow and face palette
Maybelline Hyper Curl Mascara
Ever Bilena Matte Lipstick in Toast of New York

Let's be friends!
